            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">GitHub Migrations &amp; DevOps</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm mb-4">
              End-to-end migration from Azure DevOps, BitBucket, SVN, and more ‚Äî with automation that cuts migration time from hours to minutes.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-text-muted">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent-cyan mt-0.5">‚ñ∏</span> Migration planning &amp; execution</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent-cyan mt-0.5">‚ñ∏</span> Custom automation frameworks</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent-cyan mt-0.5">‚ñ∏</span> CI/CD pipeline modernization</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent-cyan mt-0.5">‚ñ∏</span> Repository strategy &amp; governance</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 2 -->
          <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6">
            <span class="text-3xl mb-4 block">ü§ñ</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">AI &amp; Developer Productivity</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm mb-4">
              Hands-on adoption strategy for GitHub Copilot and AI-powered development workflows that measurably boost developer output and satisfaction.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-text-muted">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent-cyan mt-0.5">‚ñ∏</span> GitHub Copilot rollout &amp; training</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent-cyan mt-0.5">‚ñ∏</span> AI workflow integration</li>
