            <span class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-accent-cyan block mb-1">10+</span>
            <span class="text-text-muted text-sm">Years in Enterprise Tech</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4">Read my technical writing</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
