            <span class="text-text-primary font-heading font-semibold group-hover:text-accent-cyan transition-colors">Lessons from 500+ GitHub Migrations</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/articles/context-engineering-key-to-ai-development" class="block group bg-bg-surface border border-border-muted rounded-xl p-5 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-accent-cyan/30 hover:-translate-y-0.5">
            <span class="text-text-primary font-heading font-semibold group-hover:text-accent-cyan transition-colors">Context Engineering: The Key to AI Development</span>
