        </h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg max-w-2xl mb-10">
          Every engagement starts with a conversation. Let's discuss your challenges and explore how I can help.
        </p>
        <div class="calendly-inline-widget" data-url="https://calendly.com/htekdev/free-consultation?background_color=0a0a0f&text_color=e2e8f0&primary_color=00e5ff" style="min-width:320px;height:700px;"></div>
        <script is:inline type="text/javascript" src="https://assets.calendly.com/assets/external/widget.js" async></script>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mt-6">
          Having trouble with the widget? <a href="https://calendly.com/htekdev/free-consultation" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent-cyan hover:underline">Book directly on Calendly ‚Üí</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

